Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.19,0:01:47.99,OP_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}为了生存
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.36,0:01:51.04,OP_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}放手一搏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:55.59,OP_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}宇宙的航路在风中消散
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.64,0:01:58.86,OP_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}乐土远在数亿光年之遥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.91,0:02:02.10,OP_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}若要奋进便摒弃犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.14,0:02:05.35,OP_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}骑士们啊 踏上征程
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:09.84,OP_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}摧毁粉碎 KNIGHTS OF SIDONIA
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.89,0:02:12.96,OP_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}时运已至 KNIGHTS OF SIDONIA
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.01,0:02:16.11,OP_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}为了生存 KNIGHTS OF SIDONIA
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:20.11,OP_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}放手一搏 赢得活路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.16,0:02:23.75,OP_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}我们为谁征战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.56,0:02:30.05,OP_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}我们为谁牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.13,0:02:39.59,OP_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}未及立誓便舍身向战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.65,0:02:46.25,OP_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}不屈于重责 疲惫与命运
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.13,0:01:23.54,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}誰がために 我は征く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.18,0:01:32.10,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}誰がために 散り征くなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.29,0:01:38.69,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}何故に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.76,0:01:41.16,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}打ち砕け
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:44.39,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}時 満ちて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.19,0:01:47.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}生きるため
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.36,0:01:51.04,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}解き放て
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:55.59,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}宇宙の航路は風に消え
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:55.59,OP,NTP,0,164,0,,{\be1\fs16}そら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.64,0:01:58.86,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}安住は幾億光年先
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.91,0:02:02.10,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}突き進むなら惑うな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.14,0:02:05.35,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}いざ征かん 騎士よ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:09.84,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}打ち砕け KNIGHTS OF SIDONIA
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.89,0:02:12.96,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}時 満ちて KNIGHTS OF SIDONIA
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.01,0:02:16.11,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}生きるため KNIGHTS OF SIDONIA
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:20.11,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}解き放て 活路はこの手に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.16,0:02:23.75,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}誰がために 我は征く
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.56,0:02:30.05,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}誰がために 散り征くなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.13,0:02:39.59,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}誓い立てる間もなく この身を投げ出せ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.65,0:02:46.25,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}重責と困憊と 運命には負けじと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.65,0:02:46.25,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\fs16}さだめ
